spec_data.Name: apache-commons-compress
spec_data.Description:
The Apache Commons Compress library defines an API for working with
ar, cpio, Unix dump, tar, zip, gzip, XZ, Pack200 and bzip2 files.
In version 1.14 read-only support for Brotli decompression has been added,
but it has been removed form this package.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:37:52 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Java API for working with compressed files and archivers
